When styling UI, prefer to use already defined classes over inline styles in .jsx and .tsx files

Use props over inline styles: 
example: prefer the justifyContent prop with Horizontal elements over style={{ justifyContent: 'value' }}

instead of creating inline styles, create a css class in the css file for the feature

when making new css do not add !important

